CHARA_DEX_01_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_01_Text.text: Remember to relax, yeah? Loosen those shoulders.

CHARA_DEX_02_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_02_Text.text: Magic's a ton of fun. Being a witch is the best!

CHARA_DEX_03_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_03_Text.text: I am the Dismal King. Serve me well.

CHARA_DEX_04_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_04_Text.text: Honing one's focus is easier said than done.

CHARA_DEX_05_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_05_Text.text: I've been real into martial arts lately—workin' on my kicks!

CHARA_DEX_06_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_06_Text.text: Am I really capable of singing and dancing and such?

CHARA_DEX_07_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_07_Text.text: A true warrior's path lies in the pursuit of dual-wielding.

CHARA_DEX_08_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_08_Text.text: Stomp heavy and assuage the spirits!

CHARA_DEX_09_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_09_Text.text: I see my heart's desire as I sleep, yet wake when I know it to be a dream.

CHARA_DEX_10_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_10_Text.text: If you're gonna take your shot, you better not miss!

CHARA_DEX_11_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_11_Text.text: It would be a shame not to make the most of having a familiar around.

CHARA_DEX_12_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_12_Text.text: I am a squire. To serve a witch is my duty.

CHARA_DEX_13_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_13_Text.text: Goddesses have it tough. It's way easier being a copy!

CHARA_DEX_14_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_14_Text.text: Just do as I command and you'll win!

CHARA_DEX_15_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_15_Text.text: May the heavens above bear witness to our honor!

CHARA_DEX_16_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_16_Text.text: I must say, you are quite the interesting individual.

CHARA_DEX_17_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_17_Text.text: What do you want? I'll kill you.

CHARA_DEX_18_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_18_Text.text: Runnin' wild, runnin' free; this is the life for you and me!

CHARA_DEX_19_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_19_Text.text: A little screwin' around is fine so long as you keep training!

CHARA_DEX_25_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_25_Text.text: Iiit's Wednesday! ...Er, or I'M Wednesday, I mean. I don't know what day it is.

CHARA_DEX_26_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_26_Text.text: Don't get disappointed if I wither.

CHARA_DEX_27_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_27_Text.text: Reclaiming what I have lost is a matter of pride.

CHARA_DEX_29_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_29_Text.text: I want to discover my potential!

CHARA_DEX_30_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_30_Text.text: Being a golem isn't so bad!

CHARA_DEX_31_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_31_Text.text: Let me show you what I'm truly capable of.

CHARA_DEX_33_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_33_Text.text: Have ye anything weird to eat?

CHARA_DEX_34_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_34_Text.text: Can I truly survive away from the sea?

CHARA_DEX_36_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_36_Text.text: Need me to carry something for you?

CHARA_DEX_38_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_38_Text.text: My throat and skin are both so dry...

CHARA_DEX_39_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_39_Text.text: The air quality here is simply terrible.

CHARA_DEX_40_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_40_Text.text: I miss my life in the forest.

CHARA_DEX_41_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_41_Text.text: Yaaay! I can't wait to stuff myself!

CHARA_DEX_42_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_42_Text.text: I thought you were going to take me somewhere interesting.

CHARA_DEX_43_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_43_Text.text: Hold my calls! This scarecrow's taking another day off!

CHARA_DEX_44_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_44_Text.text: So there are worlds like this too, mmm?

CHARA_DEX_45_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_45_Text.text: Have we analyzed the enemy's combat potential?

CHARA_DEX_46_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_46_Text.text: Our legend begins! Let us sally forth!

CHARA_DEX_48_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_48_Text.text: The best offense is a strong defense!

CHARA_DEX_49_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_49_Text.text: Go on, then! There's not been nearly enough fighting!

CHARA_DEX_50_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_50_Text.text: Demonstrate now your pride as a warrior!

CHARA_DEX_52_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_52_Text.text: I will do all I can to live up to your trust.

CHARA_DEX_54_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_54_Text.text: I don't always wear the same clothes—I just own multiple copies of this outfit.

CHARA_DEX_55_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_55_Text.text: Reality's always one step ahead of me.

CHARA_DEX_56_Text.speaker: UI
CHARA_DEX_56_Text.text: Singing can bring people happiness. I truly believe that!
